title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E23 Attack! DivX
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea 
S04E23 
Attack!
First aired: March 10, 1968

After Nelson and Kowalski are captured by aliens who are plotting to destroy the Earth, Crane attempts to rescue them with the help of a peace-loving alien who wants to thwart the plans of his comrades. 

Starring Richard Basehart (Admiral Nelson), David Hedison (Capt. Crane)
Guest Cast: Skip Homeier, Kevin Hagen

Written: William Welch
Directed: Jerry Hopper
